    "body": "Thanks so much for detailed answer, it help me a lot! \r\n\r\nBut colors used in Figma does not match existing in palette. For example i need Light Desktop/Blue, and it is similar in dark theme. The closest color in out palette is Primary1 in light theme but it is differnt to figma. Here colors used in figma:\r\n| Item | Dark | Light |\r\n| ----------- | ----------- | ----------- |\r\n| Active tab button | #4360df | #4360df |\r\n| Active tab text | #ffffff | #ffffff |\r\n| Unactive tab backgound | #262d3f | #edf0fc |\r\n| Unactive tab text | #4360df | #6d84e6 |\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2522130/167085006-d068b1a4-c544-4caa-944f-383f1d364824.png)\r\nAnd whom should i ping for access to Figma? =)",
